prompt_template:
Write a detailed technical overview of laser cleaning processes specifically for {material} surfaces. Target audience: {target_audience} in {industry_focus}.

Requirements:
- Exactly {word_target} words
- Technical depth level: {technical_depth}
- Natural writing style (target: {natural_voice_target})
- Explain the physics of laser interaction with {material}
- Cover ablation thresholds, wavelength selection, and power requirements
- Include safety considerations specific to {material}
- Mention industry standards and best practices
- Do not include headers or markdown formatting
- Focus on practical technical knowledge

Content quality must meet threshold: {content_quality_threshold}
